            <div type="section" xml:id="Legislation">
                <head>Legislation</head>
                <p> The Eritrean Research and Documentation Centre is still in the process of
                    collecting and documenting its collection.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="section" xml:id="Location">
                <head>Location</head>
                <p>National Archives: PO Box 897, Asmara.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="section" xml:id="Procedures">
                <head> Procedures</head>
                <p>Visitors may directly visit the Reading Room of the Research and Documentation
                    Centre. Researchers must present a letter of introduction from their home
                    institution. </p>
            </div>
